ISLAMABAD, Jul 11 (APP):Additional Foreign Secretary (Europe) Ambassador Shafqat Ali Khan on Thursday held talks with Director (Asia & Oceania) French Foreign Ministry Ambassador Benoît Guidée here.
During the meeting, they reviewed the progress made in the implementation of Roadmap of Bilateral Cooperation, signed in 2023, ahead of the next round of Pakistan-France Bilateral Political Consultations to be held later this year, a Foreign Office statement said.
